	skos:hasTopConcept	<https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/cem/indicators/pressures> , <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/cem/indicators/controls> , <https://w3id.org/italia/env/vocab/cem/indicators/exceedances> ;
